    the_gift: 'Macha gives the *permission to curse the king\'s chariot-race when the king is making you race-while-pregnant*. The Noínden-Ulad-foundational narrative is the cosmic-permission to *refuse the impossible-performance demanded by the institutional-king*, to *collapse on the finish-line if the race kills you*, and to *die cursing the men-of-Ulster for nine generations* (the *cursing-of-the-system* as the dying-act). And the *Macha-Mongruad* gift: the cosmic-permission to be the *female-sovereign-who-defeats-the-five-male-claimants-by-direct-power-and-rules-alone*, the *foundational Irish proto-feminist permission* that has been almost-entirely-erased from popular Celtic-revival. And the *Emain-Macha-and-Ard-Macha* gift: the cosmic-permission to *name the royal seat after yourself*, to *found the place-where-you-rule and have the place-name carry your name forward through three thousand years of subsequent history* (Armagh, Northern Ireland, the ecclesiastical-capital-of-Ireland, *is named for Macha* even now, even with Saint Patrick\'s cathedral built on top — the *Macha-substrate* is foundational under everything that has been built since).',
